room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by Escape Kemah in Houston
review: Loved Escape Kemah! The owners were involved and were accommodating when we had a late guest. Room was set up very well! Will definitely be back.

room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by Escape Kemah in Houston
review: I took a bunch of little girls here for my daughter's birthday and they had the best time! I wouldn't say they were experts on focusing or problem solving (what excited 9-yo girls are?), but they enjoyed every moment of it. We appreciate the memories and fun. Looking forward to returning with ADULTS some time!

room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by Escape Kemah in Houston
review: Really fun activity to do, and not too much to spend! The rooms are challenging and really make you think, which really makes it interesting and is a great way to kill some time and bond with strangers. The location is discreet but they have signs that make it easier to find
